      "comment": "Boom colt LOUCASSO (9) makes his first appearance since a 24.5m romp in the Breeders Crown 2CG Final at this circuit and distance in December. Won seven of nine starts as a juvenile, highlighted by the G1 Protostar in Brisbane. Unbeaten fresh and should be ready to go again off two trial wins. JAZZY MELEA (8) made a good return when she raced wide but stuck on to be beaten 2m into third in a higher-graded race at this circuit and distance. Owns a good second-up record so can progress. UNIQUELY IDEAL (12) has trialled since breaking as a hot favourite last start. Can mix her form but has claims off her Kilmore win three back. Tricky draw for TEN DA TOUCH NZ (13) but he has been racing consistently.",
